                        </svg>
                        What is this?
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        This is a <strong>fully functional demonstration</strong> of an API key management system.
                        It shows how to implement secure API key generation, storage, and management using modern web technologies.
                        Keys follow a <strong>Stripe-like format</strong> (<code>sk_live_abc123...</code>) and are securely hashed before storage.
                        This demo includes a unique <strong>live database viewer</strong> to help you understand how data is stored and managed in real-time.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

